web_snippets: Jeff Westbrook is a TV writer best known for his work on The Simpsons and Futurama, for which he is a three-time winner of the WGA Award.
Jeff Westbrook is a writer for The Simpsons. He has also written for Futurama. Prior to becoming a TV writer, Westbrook was a successful algorithms researcher.
Jeff Westbrook *89 didn't plan on becoming an academic. Then again, he didn't plan on becoming a writer for Futurama and The Simpsons, either.
